reviewText: Amber caulder u do realize those were specialze right

Episodes were missing. The transition from David Tennant to Matt Smith was missing. The last episode with the Master is not there. Spelling errors all over the DVDs'. Double check before you buy this set. Spent almost $300 on this set and not everything to Season Nine is included [recent Doctor Who].
Was very surprised to get the whole 9th season!
I was very happy with it, the only thing is that the special episodes were not included. Overall, very happy.
We love us some Doctor Who!
